你坐好 放轻松
Well, you sit back, relax

368
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:14,800
尽享回到童年的快乐之旅吧
and enjoy a beloved childhood memory.

369
00:16:17,860 --> 00:16:21,160
看见那边那座小屋没?
You see that cabin there?

370
00:16:21,160 --> 00:16:24,360
他们是私自占用印第安人的土地
I read they were illegally squatting on Indian land.

371
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:26,400
是啊
Yeah.

372
00:16:26,400 --> 00:16:28,660
个人认为 我们对印第安原住民的
Personally, I think what we did

373
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:31,000
所作所为大错特错
to the Native Americans was wrong,

374
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:33,600
但这毕竟是你最爱的片子 不是我的
but this is your favorite show, not mine.

375
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:36,760
看看小萝拉·英格斯
Oh, look at little Laura Ingalls,

376
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:39,230
吃着那块花生黄油三明治
eating that peanut butter sandwich.

377
00:16:39,230 --> 00:16:40,760
花生黄油?!
Peanut butter?!

378
00:16:40,760 --> 00:16:43,560
嗬!
Huh!

379
00:16:43,560 --> 00:16:45,830
这就怪了 因为花生黄油
That's strange, since peanut butter

380
00:16:45,830 --> 00:16:48,630
直到上世纪初才问世
wasn't introduced until the early 1900s.

381
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:53,330
我要是事先知道这是部穿越剧
If I knew this show was about time travel,

382
00:16:53,330 --> 00:16:56,100
我早就来看了
I would have watched it much sooner.

383
00:16:58,800 --> 00:17:00,100
你在报复我
You're trying to get back at me

384
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:02,130
就为了我对"夺宝奇兵"的评价
for what I said about Raiders of the Lost Ark.

385
00:17:02,130 --> 00:17:03,730
胡扯 怎么可能
That's silly.

386
00:17:03,730 --> 00:17:06,700
简直跟贝克医生拥有电话这件事一样胡扯
Almost as silly as Dr. Baker having a telephone,

387
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:08,130
因为那个时期
since telephones only existed

388
00:17:08,130 --> 00:17:09,960
电话只在大城市里才有
in large cities at that time.

389
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:12,460
这倒更像是部"大荒诞之家"
This is more like Little House on the Preposterous.

390
00:17:14,460 --> 00:17:17,200
Sheldon 我们在谈恋爱
Sheldon, we're in a relationship.

391
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:19,330
你生气的时候 要跟我直说
When you get angry, just tell me.

392
00:17:19,330 --> 00:17:21,500
没必要以牙还牙地报复
You don't need to seek revenge.

393
00:17:21,500 --> 00:17:24,060
真的吗?
Are you sure?

394
00:17:25,200 --> 00:17:26,900
每次我爸彻夜不归的时候
Every time my dad stayed out all night,

395
00:17:26,900 --> 00:17:30,300
妈妈都会把仓鼠屎偷偷混进他的口嚼烟草里面
my mom would put hamster poop in his chewing tobacco.

396
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,860
不管 反正咱们之间不是这样的
Well, that's not how we're going to do it.

397
00:17:33,860 --> 00:17:36,060
好吧
Fine.

398
00:17:36,060 --> 00:17:37,500
我很生你的气
I'm mad at you.

399
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:39,960
不光是因为你毁了我的"夺宝奇兵"
Not only did you ruin Raiders for me,

400
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:41,860
你甚至毁了整个系列
you may have ruined the whole franchise.

401
00:17:41,860 --> 00:17:43,930
除了第四部
Except for the fourth one,

402
00:17:43,930 --> 00:17:46,100
那部自己就已经够糟的了
which was bad before you got your mitts on it.

403
00:17:47,760 --> 00:17:49,060
我... 我当时不该那么说的
I... I shouldn't have said it.

404
00:17:49,060 --> 00:17:50,060
我道歉
I'm sorry.

405
00:17:50,060 --> 00:17:52,000
谢谢你
Thank you.

406
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,330
感觉好点了吗?
Do you feel better?

407
00:17:53,330 --> 00:17:55,000
嗯
Yes.

408
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:57,530
但如果我告诉你这个之后我会更开心的 
But not as good as I'm going to when I tell you

409
00:17:57,530 --> 00:17:59,760
你亲爱的加菲猫根本没道理讨厌周一
that your precious Garfield has no reason to hate Mondays.

410
00:18:00,900 --> 00:18:03,200
他是只猫 他又不用上班
He's a cat. He doesn't have a job.

411
00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:11,430
嘿 我刚刚... 什么情况?
Hey, I was just... what is happening?

412
00:18:12,660 --> 00:18:14,500
噢 就是犒劳你一下
Oh, just a little treat.

413
00:18:14,500 --> 00:18:16,160
我知道最近一提到你妈
I know you've been feeling really bad

414
00:18:16,160 --> 00:18:17,600
你就很难过
about your mom lately.

415
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:19,460
哦 我是很难过
Oh, oh, I have.

416
00:18:19,460 --> 00:18:21,060
悲痛欲绝
So bad.

417
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:23,060
我想让你高兴高兴
And I wanted to make you feel better,

418
00:18:23,060 --> 00:18:25,230
所以我为你准备了惊喜大礼包
so I planned something very special for you.

419
00:18:25,230 --> 00:18:26,230
嗯哼
Uh-huh, uh-huh.

420
00:18:26,230 --> 00:18:29,030
我已经惊喜得有反应了
I can already feel it working.

421
00:18:30,330 --> 00:18:32,600
你好 Leonard
Hello, Leonard.

422
00:18:34,330 --> 00:18:36,530
妈?!
Mom?!

423
00:18:36,530 --> 00:18:40,030
我听说你最近为了在情感上控制你的女友
I understand you have been whining about my parenting

424
00:18:40,030 --> 00:18:42,600
一直对我的抚养方式哭哭啼啼 抱怨个不停
in order to emotionally manipulate your girlfriend.

425
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:44,500
我... 呃...
I... uh...

426
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:45,860
Bernadette都告诉我了
Bernadette told me everything.

427
00:18:45,860 --> 00:18:47,800
现在你左边右边哪边都甭想要了
Now you don't get the left or the right.

428
00:18:50,360 --> 00:18:51,700
咱们来探讨一下
Let's discuss

429
00:18:51,700 --> 00:18:53,730
你为何依然将我
why you continue to involve me

430
00:18:53,730 --> 00:18:55,130
扯进你的性生活
in your sex life.

431
00:18:55,130 --> 00:18:56,330
别了 求你了 妈妈
Oh, please, Mommy.

432
00:18:56,330 --> 00:18:58,930
别了 妈妈
No, Mommy.

433
00:18:58,930 --> 00:19:00,230
你六岁那年
When you were six years old,

434
00:19:00,230 --> 00:19:03,060
走进房间 撞见我跟你爸一丝不挂
you walked in on me and your father naked.

435
00:19:04,430 --> 00:19:05,860
我当时正用你新买的乒乓球拍
I was swatting his bottom

436
00:19:05,860 --> 00:19:09,000
拍打他的屁股
with your brand new Ping Pong paddle.

437
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:15,130
原来我当时不是在做梦?
I didn't dream that?

438
00:19:15,130 --> 00:19:17,960
你当时感觉如何?
How did that make you feel?

439
00:19:17,960 --> 00:19:19,660
Penny 快回来!
Penny, come back!

440
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:22,160
我现在是真的难过了!
I'm sad for real now!

441
00:19:23,460 --> 00:19:25,160
在过去两小时当中
In the last two hours,

442
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:27,760
有162个女人看了我们的资料
162 women have read our profiles.

443
00:19:27,760 --> 00:19:29,560
多少人给咱们留言了?
How many of them have sent us messages?

444
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:30,960
- 加起来?  - 嗯
- Combined?  - Yes.

445
00:19:30,960 --> 00:19:33,030
零个
Zero.

446
00:19:35,260 --> 00:19:37,130
老兄 这... 这简直太残忍了
Dude, this is... this is brutal.

447
00:19:37,130 --> 00:19:40,230
我以前从没受过这样的气
I don't think I've ever felt so rejected.

448
00:19:40,230 --> 00:19:41,960
我可是救助过一只狗
And I had a rescue dog

449
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:44,360
那狗却跑走了的人啊
who ran back to the pound.

450
00:19:47,060 --> 00:19:48,260
简直不可能更糟了
This is the worst.

451
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:49,330
要是咱们想被放倒
If we're gonna get shot down,

452
00:19:49,330 --> 00:19:50,730
还不如跟以前一样
we might as well just go to a bar

453
00:19:50,730 --> 00:19:51,900
直接去酒吧
and do it old school.

454
00:19:51,900 --> 00:19:54,130
直视她们 看她还好意思拒绝
And make them look us in the eye.

455
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:55,700
就是 怎么都比这样强
Yeah, anything is better than this.

456
00:19:55,700 --> 00:19:57,300
你好啊
Hello.

457
00:19:57,300 --> 00:19:58,500
对你没兴趣
Not interested.

458
00:20:01,230 --> 00:20:03,300
我错了 这样更糟
I was wrong. This is worse.

459
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:18,660
等等... 要不是因为印第安纳·琼斯
Wait, wait... if it wasn't for Indiana Jones,

460
00:20:18,660 --> 00:20:20,760
约柜怎么会出现在仓库!
the ark would never have ended up at the warehouse!

461
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:22,700
没错儿!
That's true!

462
00:20:22,700 --> 00:20:24,800
是他带上约柜
He collected and delivered the ark

463
00:20:24,800 --> 00:20:26,800
