to the proper authorities for filing.

464
00:20:26,800 --> 00:20:27,700
大英雄啊!
Like a hero!

465
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:29,760
就是! 说得好!
Yeah! Yes! Right!

466
00:20:31,530 --> 00:20:32,730
不过 理论上讲
Although, technically,

467
00:20:32,730 --> 00:20:34,260
他本来应该把约柜
Indy was supposed to take the ark

468
00:20:34,260 --> 00:20:35,500
带到一座博物馆给人研究的
to a museum to be studied.

469
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:37,260
可他连这种小事都没做到
He couldn't even get that done.

